I see no reason to move my vote if people give no explanatons for their votes. Rmp could be scum, bub is town, and I see no reason to think Mirari is town. The normalcy thing could have pretty easily been faked I think. It's true that the sig thing didn't have much motivation behind faking but it kinda adds more to the story.

@Telo Interesting reads. I appreciate the 'i don't know' this time. Makes me much happier. Also the colors make it easier to read. Very Pro-town from where I'm at.<br>
<br>
@mrbungle I keep forgetting that you are even in the game. I'd really like to see your reads.

@reck Like scum couldn't make an outside qt to look town? I don't see your point. I would've done the exact same thing as scum to either be able to change my position quickly, or demonstrate a town thought process.<br>
